-- Barbell
('Decline Close-Grip Bench Press', 'Chest', 'Lie on a decline bench with a narrow grip inside shoulder-width. Lower the bar to your lower chest, keeping elbows tucked. Press to lockout. The close grip shifts emphasis to the inner chest and triceps.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Low Incline Barbell Press', 'Chest', 'Set the bench to 15-20 degrees — just barely inclined. Unrack and lower the bar to the upper chest. Press to lockout. This angle hits the upper chest without over-involving the front delts.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Shoulders','Triceps'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Spoto Press', 'Chest', 'Perform a bench press but pause the bar 1-2 inches above your chest, eliminating any bounce. Hold for a beat, then press explosively. This builds strength off the chest and improves control.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'advanced', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Pin Press', 'Chest', 'Set the safety pins in a rack at chest height. Press the barbell from a dead stop on the pins to lockout. Each rep starts from a complete stop, eliminating the stretch reflex and building raw pressing power.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'advanced', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Barbell Floor Press', 'Chest', 'Lie on the floor with the barbell in a rack or blocks. Lower until your triceps touch the floor, pause, then press up. The limited range of motion focuses on lockout strength and reduces shoulder stress.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Cambered Bar Bench Press', 'Chest', 'Use a cambered bar on a flat bench. The bar path dips below chest level, increasing the range of motion and chest stretch. Press to lockout with control. Excellent for building chest size through greater ROM.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'advanced', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),

-- Dumbbell
('Decline Dumbbell Press', 'Chest', 'Lie on a decline bench holding dumbbells at chest level. Press up to full extension, squeezing the chest at the top. Lower with control. The decline targets the lower chest fibres.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Neutral-Grip Dumbbell Press', 'Chest', 'Lie flat and press dumbbells with palms facing each other. This grip is easier on the shoulders and shifts emphasis toward the inner chest. Press to full extension and squeeze at the top.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Single-Arm Dumbbell Bench Press', 'Chest', 'Lie flat holding one dumbbell. Press with one arm while bracing your core to resist rotation. This variation builds unilateral pressing strength and core stability. Complete all reps on one side before switching.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders','Core'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Dumbbell Around-the-World', 'Chest', 'Lie flat with dumbbells at your sides, arms extended. Sweep both dumbbells in a wide arc overhead, then reverse the motion back to the start. Keep a slight bend in the elbows throughout. This targets the full chest through a long range of motion.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Shoulders'], 'isolation', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Dumbbell Pullover', 'Chest', 'Lie across a bench with only your upper back supported. Hold one dumbbell overhead with both hands. Lower it behind your head in an arc, feeling the stretch across the chest and lats. Pull it back over your chest.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Back','Shoulders'], 'isolation', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Close-Grip Dumbbell Press', 'Chest', 'Lie flat and press two dumbbells together, touching throughout the movement. This constant inward pressure hammers the inner chest. Press to lockout and squeeze hard at the top.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Triceps'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Decline Dumbbell Flye', 'Chest', 'Lie on a decline bench and perform flyes, lowering the dumbbells with a slight elbow bend until you feel a deep stretch. Squeeze them back together over the lower chest. Control the descent.', 'Dumbbell', ARRAY['Shoulders'], 'isolation', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),

-- Machine
('Machine Incline Press', 'Chest', 'Sit in an incline chest press machine. Press the handles forward and up to full extension, focusing on the upper chest. Return with control, feeling a stretch at the bottom.', 'Machine', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Machine Decline Press', 'Chest', 'Sit in a decline chest press machine. Press the handles forward and down to full extension. The decline angle shifts emphasis to the lower chest. Control the return.', 'Machine', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Machine Chest Fly', 'Chest', 'Sit in a chest fly machine with arms at chest height. Bring the handles together in front of your chest, squeezing hard at the peak. Return slowly to feel the stretch.', 'Machine', ARRAY['Shoulders'], 'isolation', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Assisted Dip Machine (Chest)', 'Chest', 'Use the assisted dip machine with a forward lean to target the chest. Select counterweight assistance and perform dips, leaning forward to emphasize the pecs over the triceps.', 'Machine', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Smith Machine Bench Press', 'Chest', 'Lie on a flat bench under the Smith machine. Unrack and lower the bar to mid-chest, then press up. The fixed bar path allows you to focus on chest activation without balancing.', 'Machine', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Smith Machine Incline Press', 'Chest', 'Set a bench to 30-45 degrees under the Smith machine. Lower to the upper chest and press up. The guided path lets you push harder on upper chest without stability concerns.', 'Machine', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),

-- Cable
('Cable Chest Press', 'Chest', 'Set cables at chest height. Step forward into a stagger stance and press both handles forward, squeezing the chest at full extension. Return with control. Cables provide constant tension throughout.', 'Cable', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('High Cable Crossover', 'Chest', 'Set both pulleys to the highest position. Step forward and bring the handles down and together in front of your hips. Squeeze the lower chest hard at the bottom. Return under control.', 'Cable', ARRAY['Shoulders'], 'isolation', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Mid Cable Crossover', 'Chest', 'Set both pulleys at shoulder height. Step forward and bring the handles together directly in front of your chest. This mid-angle evenly targets the entire chest. Squeeze at the midpoint.', 'Cable', ARRAY['Shoulders'], 'isolation', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Single-Arm Cable Chest Press', 'Chest', 'Set one cable at chest height. Press forward with one arm while bracing your core against rotation. This unilateral pressing variation builds balance and core stability alongside chest strength.', 'Cable', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders','Core'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Cable Pullover', 'Chest', 'Stand facing away from a high pulley with a straight bar or rope. Pull the attachment from overhead down to your hips in an arc with straight arms. Squeeze the chest and lats at the bottom.', 'Cable', ARRAY['Back','Core'], 'isolation', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),

-- Bodyweight
('Decline Push-Up', 'Chest', 'Place your feet on a bench or box and your hands on the floor. Perform push-ups with your body at a decline angle. This shifts more load to the upper chest and shoulders.', 'Bodyweight', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders','Core'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Wide Push-Up', 'Chest', 'Place your hands wider than shoulder-width. Perform push-ups with a wider arc, increasing the stretch across the chest. Keep your core tight and avoid flaring elbows past 90 degrees.', 'Bodyweight', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders','Core'], 'push', 'beginner', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Close-Grip Push-Up', 'Chest', 'Place hands inside shoulder-width, forming a diamond or narrow triangle shape. Perform push-ups keeping elbows tucked to your sides. This shifts emphasis to the inner chest and triceps.', 'Bodyweight', ARRAY['Triceps','Core'], 'push', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Archer Push-Up', 'Chest', 'Start in a wide push-up position. Lower toward one hand while extending the opposite arm out straight. Press back up. Alternate sides each rep. This is a progression toward one-arm push-ups.', 'Bodyweight', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders','Core'], 'push', 'advanced', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Plyometric Push-Up', 'Chest', 'Perform a push-up explosively so your hands leave the floor at the top. Land softly and immediately descend into the next rep. This builds explosive pressing power and fast-twitch chest activation.', 'Bodyweight', ARRAY['Triceps','Shoulders','Core'], 'plyometric', 'advanced', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),

