('Snatch-Grip Deadlift', 'Back', 'Use a wide snatch-width grip on the barbell. Deadlift from the floor with this wider grip, which increases range of motion and upper back engagement. Keep your chest up and lats tight.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Glutes','Hamstrings','Core','Shoulders'], 'hinge', 'advanced', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
