('Barbell Seal Row', 'Back', 'Lie face-down on an elevated bench with a barbell below you. Row the bar to the underside of the bench. The prone position eliminates all momentum, isolating the back completely.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Biceps','Shoulders'], 'pull', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
('Wide-Grip Bent-Over Row', 'Back', 'Perform a bent-over row with a grip wider than shoulder-width. This wider grip shifts emphasis to the upper back and rear delts. Pull to the lower chest and squeeze the shoulder blades together.', 'Barbell', ARRAY['Biceps','Shoulders'], 'pull', 'intermediate', false, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'),
